<p class="box" style="text-align: center;">To complete your node installation choose your operating system and copy&paste lines in a root shell</p>

<h4>CentOS</h4>
<pre>
<% if request.ssl? -%>
wget --no-check-certificate -qO - https://<%=Setting.plugin_initr['initr_ip']%>/install/centos/<%=@node.name%> | /bin/sh
</pre>
<p>On CentOS you need to use --no-check-certificate because our CA is not yet included in /etc/pki/tls/certs/ca-bundle.crt</p>
<% else -%>
wget -qO - http://<%=Setting.plugin_initr['initr_ip']%>/install/centos/<%=@node.name%> | /bin/sh
</pre>
<% end -%>

<h4>Debian</h4>
<pre>
<% if request.ssl? -%>
apt-get install ca-certificates && wget -qO - https://<%=Setting.plugin_initr['initr_ip']%>/install/debian/<%=@node.name%> | /bin/sh
<% else -%>
wget -qO - http://<%=Setting.plugin_initr['initr_ip']%>/install/debian/<%=@node.name%> | /bin/sh
<% end -%>
</pre>

